reviewText: It was fine won't play on blue ray but plays on computer then I stream on to my tv
Great product, accurate & clear product description, fast & excellent service & communication

Pleasant series set in picturesque Derbyshire. The actors are all good; the scripts are sometimes a bit lacking in the 'grit'  that you see in medical series these days ; no cranky doctors snorting drugs here !
It has been a few decades since I last saw this series.  Loved it!  Beautiful scenery and great acting!  Thank you!

I really loved the first series of peak practice it brought back a lot of old memories for me  I used to with peak practice with my mum and dad I hoping to buy series 2 and series 3 of peak practice very soon
